*Bude* li ovo sneg, neću moći da izađem. (If this is snow, I won't be able to go out.)

*Budila* se još uvek u osam ujutru. (She was still waking up at eight in the morning.)

*Biće* li vruće sutra? (Will it be hot tomorrow?)

*Budite* strpljivi. (Be patient.)

*Budući* da je hladno, zgrabila sam zimsku jaknu. (Since it was cold, I grabbed a winter jacket.)